assets.map

Class Map

  • java.lang.Object
    • assets.map.Map
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    EasiestLevel, EnemyRoom, Level0, Level1, Level2, Level3, Maze1, Room1, Room2

    public abstract class Map
extends java.lang.Object
    A class to represent a map in the game. A map is generated using a Buffered image from the Assets class and a SpriteSheet to define the images for all the tiles.
    Author:
    Kabir Batra
